Description: Fragments of papyrus with 8 lines of hieratic text, in black ink on recto. Part of the Book of the Temple, same ms as Vienna Aeg 4851b; P. Berlin 23048; P. Louvre 10621.
Curator's comments: To be published by Joachim Friedrich Quack (Heidelberg)
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380795) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380795)
